headline: Henry Schein One Unveils Industry-first Natively Embedded Voice Workflow at 2025 Greater New York Dental Meeting
summary: AMERICAN FORK, Utah, November 25, 2025--Coming off the heels of its announcement with Amazon Web Services, Henry Schein One, the leading provider of global dental technology, today unveils natively embedded AI and automation workflows. This includes Voice Notes, which helps practices close revenue gaps through clean claims, and modernize more effectively.
